New Delhi, the 31st January 1966.
The undersigned is directed to circulate, for information,
the attached list of the Members of the Council of Ministers, as
on January 29, 1966.
(D .P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary,

(D .P. Chopra)

O.P. Chopra)
